Why: Improve security: rotate/refresh tokens, set secure cookies, prevent session fixation.
Files: auth.ts, app/api/auth/*.
Steps:
Review cookie flags (HttpOnly, Secure, SameSite).
Add token rotation or short-lived JWT + refresh endpoint.
Add rate limiting for login/signup endpoints.
ETA: 4–8 hours.


